    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean, mint-condition vehicle. Interior and exterior show very minimal wear, and it appears to have been extremely well cared for. A strong option for someone looking for a very clean, well-kept car.",
