    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Older vehicle in poor overall condition and priced accordingly. This is best suited for someone looking for a project, repair candidate, or possible parts car rather than a clean daily driver. Expect heavy cosmetic wear, age-related deterioration, and a strong chance it will need mechanical work and deferred maintenance addressed. Interior, exterior, and overall presentation show significant use. Please come with realistic expectations \u2014 this is an honest as-is sale for a buyer who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept vehicle in good overall condition. The exterior presents nicely with only normal light wear for its age, and the interior is tidy and cared for with some minor signs of use but nothing excessive. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that should appeal to someone looking for a dependable, good-quality vehicle without paying mint-condition money. Expect a car that shows well, feels well maintained, and is ready to enjoy with the usual small imperfections you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Honest, affordable transportation with solid value for the right buyer. This vehicle is best suited for someone seeking a practical, low-cost option and willing to appreciate it for what it is: a dependable way to get from point A to point B without a big investment. A smart buy for commuters, first-time drivers, or anyone needing straightforward mobility at an accessible price.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a handy project to tinker with. It\u2019s got the kind of honest character you\u2019d expect at this price point, and it could make a great first car, commuter, or spare vehicle. If you\u2019re after something cheap, cheerful, and worth a look, this one could be a great fit.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with strong enthusiast upside. This car presents as a well-used example, but the core package is still appealing: solid-running powertrain, responsive steering feel, and a chassis that remains fundamentally composed on the road. It starts, moves, stops, and offers a great foundation for someone looking for an affordable entry point, weekend tinkering platform, or budget performance-inspired build. Cosmetic wear and age-related needs are present, but that also means you can improve it your way without paying collector money up front. If you want a mechanically honest car with usable bones and real potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap ride. Runs, drives, gets the job done. Not pretty, priced right. Solid beater or project. First cash takes it.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car that turns an ordinary driveway into the start of a story. It has undeniable presence, a lived-in charm, and the sort of character you simply can\u2019t manufacture. Perfect for the hands-on driver, weekend tinkerer, or anyone looking for an affordable ride with personality, it offers a rare chance to own something with soul and make it your own. Whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly daily, a project with promise, or a vehicle that still knows how to make an impression, this one brings plenty of opportunity at a price that leaves room for your vision.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle that offers dependable transportation at an accessible price. This car shows its age and is best suited for buyers who value affordability, utility, and an honest opportunity to get on the road without overspending. A smart choice for a commuter, backup vehicle, or project-minded owner looking for solid value.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    }
